WEBVTT

00:06:00.370 --> 00:06:01.520
unaweza kukimbia.

00:06:02.395 --> 00:06:04.260
Na kama huwezi kukimbia,

00:06:04.284 --> 00:06:05.434
unaweza kutembea.

00:06:06.133 --> 00:06:08.125
Lakini kama huwezi kutembea,

00:06:08.149 --> 00:06:09.626
unaweza kutambaa.

00:06:10.331 --> 00:06:12.593
Lakini vyovyote, namna yoyote itavyogharimu,

00:06:12.617 --> 00:06:13.950
endelea kusonga mbele."

00:06:14.831 --> 00:06:17.172
Kwa hiyo nikawa na shauku ya kusonga mbele.

00:06:17.196 --> 00:06:19.950
Bado nina hii shauku ya kusonga mbele katika kila ninalofanya.

00:06:19.974 --> 00:06:23.418
Kwa sababu nahisi njia pekee tunayoweza kubadili jamii yetu,

00:06:23.442 --> 00:06:25.718
njia pekee tunayoweza kubadili mfumo wa haki --

00:06:25.742 --> 00:06:27.751
ambao umekuwa na maboresho makubwa nchini kwetu --

00:06:27.775 --> 00:06:29.402
ni kusaidia kuweka mifumo sawa.